display="inline"><![CDATA[Y_\bullet ]]></fr:tex> is the complement of a normal crossing divisor in a smooth and proper simplicial scheme <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\bar {Y}_\bullet ]]></fr:tex>, and is a proper hypercover of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex>.
    We have ((II) of <fr:ref
